snippet.title: Cosmo's Delivery and Logistics Trailer
snippet.description:
Cosmo's Delivery and Logistics is a poker deck-builder set in space. Cheat, swindle, and bamboozle your way through little Asteroid County’s ubiquitous poker tables, learning new tricks, upgrading your truck, and exploring local landmarks along the way!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2479950/Cosmos_Delivery_and_Logistics/
